    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/3ba8ace2aa603e04c045df0ce0138f0f.poster.avif?t=1766066506\" width=1000 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/3ba8ace2aa603e04c045df0ce0138f0f.webm?t=1766066506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Welcome, Wanderers.</strong><br>Settle in the storm-swept Crosslands, a realm between the human and spirit worlds. Make your home in a vast, ever-changing shared landscape that empowers and fosters friendship, kindness, and community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Perhaps you’ll harvest rare flowers, join a fishing tournament, or play songs to passersby from a rooftop at sunset. Every day brings endless possibilities for kind, creative interactions with new friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/bff98ddd1f34f8b78da2dd458ead7b92.poster.avif?t=1766066506\" width=1170 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/bff98ddd1f34f8b78da2dd458ead7b92.webm?t=1766066506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/bff98ddd1f34f8b78da2dd458ead7b92.mp4?t=1766066506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/5bfc9afd1e17f7dd9da8f645952aebe2.poster.avif?t=1766066506\" width=1000 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/5bfc9afd1e17f7dd9da8f645952aebe2.webm?t=1766066506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Join a Waystation – a customizable village that grows with a community of players. Together, you’ll build, decorate, fortify and sustain your home. Visit other Waystations to play with new friends and explore new sights. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/4e277bd5e6ef12d0ab01decdb2f66978.poster.avif?t=1766066506\" width=1170 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/4e277bd5e6ef12d0ab01decdb2f66978.webm?t=1766066506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/4e277bd5e6ef12d0ab01decdb2f66978.mp4?t=1766066506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/8a7f4225fb268d4f80277d372137f03c.poster.avif?t=1766066506\" width=1000 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/8a7f4225fb268d4f80277d372137f03c.webm?t=1766066506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Curate your social experience with a unique friendship system. By leveling up your friendships, you can unlock proximity chat, two-player emotes, teleportation, gift giving, and much more. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/ea5917342b964c755253150da05f93ab.poster.avif?t=1766066506\" width=1170 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/ea5917342b964c755253150da05f93ab.webm?t=1766066506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/ea5917342b964c755253150da05f93ab.mp4?t=1766066506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/485dbd0cf76bc4c09b5dcd37c3d3f78c.poster.avif?t=1766066506\" width=1000 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/485dbd0cf76bc4c09b5dcd37c3d3f78c.webm?t=1766066506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Regular storms tear apart structures and draw in lonely spirits. By performing acts of kindness and leaving offerings that restore Waystation Beacons, you can hold the storms at bay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/746aae7896801457edaf88653085074d.poster.avif?t=1766066506\" width=1170 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/746aae7896801457edaf88653085074d.webm?t=1766066506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/746aae7896801457edaf88653085074d.mp4?t=1766066506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/4a53fcda07a4e59f8a48ba2498521f73.poster.avif?t=1766066506\" width=1000 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/4a53fcda07a4e59f8a48ba2498521f73.webm?t=1766066506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">As you explore, you’ll meet people and spirits who need help. With patience and kindness, they’ll begin to reveal more about themselves, gifting items and stories. Over time, you’ll understand the curious ways spirits communicate.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/a46dabccad484c44b4509d347c21af26.poster.avif?t=1766066506\" width=1170 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/a46dabccad484c44b4509d347c21af26.webm?t=1766066506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/a46dabccad484c44b4509d347c21af26.mp4?t=1766066506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/1514c382180941c30e8274a453784b8b.poster.avif?t=1766066506\" width=1000 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/1514c382180941c30e8274a453784b8b.webm?t=1766066506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Unleash your unique creative vision. Manage, upgrade, decorate, and use your own house as you see fit. <br>It may even come with a tiny  roommate. 🐻</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/bded6fe9a753a8ae650e5fabf6c911fd.poster.avif?t=1766066506\" width=1170 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/bded6fe9a753a8ae650e5fabf6c911fd.webm?t=1766066506\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321960/extras/bded6fe9a753a8ae650e5fabf6c911fd.mp4?t=1766066506\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">⟢ Befriend villagers, little bears, and other players</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">⟢ Unique friendship levelling system with fun perks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">⟢ Solo and Co-op activities, building, puzzles, and timed events</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">⟢ Aid mysterious spirits, learn their ways</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">⟢ Glide, climb, and explore a vast, ever-changing wilderness</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">⟢ Expressive character and home customisation</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">⟢ Sensational seasonal soundtracks<br><br><br><strong><i>Please note that game progress does not transfer between the Steam and mobile versions of Spirit Crossing.</i></strong></p>",
